                <note rend="inline" type="source">825.00/675: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Ambassador in Chile</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Culbertson</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Acting Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Santiago</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1931-08-06T10:00:00-05:00"
                            >August 6, 1931—10 a.m.</date>
                        <lb/>[Received 11:02 a.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>87. Department’s telegram No. 32, August 1, noon. Presidential elections have
                    been called for October 4th.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Culbertson</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
